assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: NANSO Transport Co.,Ltd. provides logistics services in Japan. The company provides automobile, special combined, railway, and nursing care transportation comprising product management and delivery, and storage and transportation of beverage products and dangerous goods as well as lunch delivery services. It also offers transport handling warehousing; distribution processing; in-factory work; general worker dispatch; customs clearance; sheet metal painting; parking lot; car and motorcycle maintenance; human resources outsourcing; and security services. In addition, the company engages in real estate transactions and leasing; building cleaning; non-life insurance agency; life insurance soliciting; sale of petroleum; and incidental businesses. Further, it is involved in the construction of local office buildings and housing, as well as repairing; and drinking water production assistance, labeling, packaging, and delivery. NANSO Transport Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1942 and is headquartered in Togane, Japan.
